rm(list = ls())

library(mdgsa)
library(clusterProfiler)
library(enrichplot)
library(fgsea)
library(org.Dr.eg.db)
library(ggplot2)
library(pathview)
library(KEGGREST)
library(tidyverse)
library(limma)
library(edgeR)
library(xlsx)

Sacamos la lista de los genes y las rutas de KEGG.

keys <- keys(org.Dr.eg.db, keytype="SYMBOL")
r_kegg <- AnnotationDbi::select(org.Dr.eg.db, keys=keys,
                                columns=c("SYMBOL", "PATH"),
                                keytype="SYMBOL")
r_kegg <- na.exclude(r_kegg)
r_kegg <- r_kegg[,c(2,1)]

dre_pathways <- keggList("pathway", "dre") %>% 
    tibble(pathway = names(.), description = .)

path_ids <- str_split_i(dre_pathways$pathway, "dre", 2)
path_descriptions <- str_split_i(dre_pathways$description, " -", 1)
dre_pathways$pathway <- path_ids
dre_pathways$description <- path_descriptions

Contrastes

72 hpf vs 48 hpf

load("tt_72_48.RData")
diffexp <- tt_72_48$table

# differential expressed genes
print("Número de genes significativos")
## [1] "Número de genes significativos"
table(diffexp$FDR < 0.05)
## 
## FALSE  TRUE 
## 14675  3160
sig.genes <- diffexp[diffexp$FDR < 0.05, ]

 

Top genes

threshold <- 1.5
top <- sig.genes[sig.genes$logFC > threshold, ]
top_genes <- row.names(top)

writeLines(as.character(top_genes), con = "72_48_top_genes_list.txt", sep = "\n")

BP

# load("data/oraTop.RData")
oraTop <- enrichGO(gene        = top_genes,
                 OrgDb         = org.Dr.eg.db,
                 keyType       = 'SYMBOL',
                 ont           = "BP",
                 pAdjustMethod = "BH",
                 qvalueCutoff  = 0.05)
# save(oraTop, file = "data/oraTop.RData")

print(paste0("Número de funciones significativas: ", dim(oraTop)[1]))
## [1] "Número de funciones significativas: 14"
if (dim(oraTop)[1] > 0) {
  oraTop_table <- oraTop@result[oraTop@result$p.adjust < 0.05,c("ID","p.adjust")]
  write.table(oraTop_table, file = "top_bp_1.txt", sep = "\t", row.names = FALSE, quote = FALSE)
  write.xlsx(oraTop@result, file = "funciones_72_48_bp_ups.xlsx")
  dotplot(oraTop,
          showCategory = 20,
          x = "geneRatio",
          font.size = 6)
  }

MF

  write.xlsx(oraBottom@result, file = "funciones_Adulto_120_mf_downs.xlsx")
  dotplot(oraBottom,
          showCategory = 20,
          x = "geneRatio",
          font.size = 6)
  }
